    "name": "Knight",
    "role": "defender",
    "info": {
      "flavor": "<p>Knight pilots live for the thrill of battle. They engage high value targets in a compulsory duel, locking themselves in a fight to the death. Their mighty blows leave their opponents open to supporting fire from the Knight’s compatriots.</p>",
      "tactics": "<p>The Knight challenges an opponent to a <b><span style='font-variant: small-caps;'>Compelled Duel</span></b>. However, this proves to be far from a fair fight, as <b><span style='font-variant: small-caps;'>Champion’s Greatsword</span></b> leaves the Knight’s opponent vulnerable to outside interference and <b><span style='font-variant: small-caps;'>Templar’s Shield</span></b> impedes their attacks. While durable, the Knight is easy to hit with both weapons and tech attacks.</p>"
